-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project — Hybrid R-Sentry — was designed and built as a cybersecurity
capstone, combining behavioral ransomware detection, adaptive canary defense,
AI-powered threat classification, and automated containment into a single
cohesive system.

For questions, collaborations, or vulnerability reports, contact:
